
label s107:
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_01.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/09.mp3'
    
    "In my dream, I'm staring at the moon."
    
    "I can't remember where I am or why I'm looking up at it."
    
    "Maybe I looked up into the night sky not wanting to see anything, and the moon happened to be there."
    
    "My back creaks."
    
    "Coursing through my veins is an image of coldness."
    
    "A solitary darkness that makes me dizzy."
    
    "A radiant moon that sickens my heart."
    
    ".... Strange."
    
    "The overwhelming coldness feels more like a sense of nostalgia."
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_11.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"---Shiki-sama.\""
    
    ".... I can hear Hisui's voice mingling with the morning light."
    
    "\"---Shiki-sama, it is time."
    
    "Please wake up.\""
    
    "Her inflectionless voice awakens me."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40E.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"------\""
    
    "As soon as I wake up, terrible things enter my vision."
    
    "I get a headache like I was just shot in the head."
    
    "\"Ah----\""
    
    "I almost lose my just awakened consciousness."
    
    "Before I fade away completely, I quickly grab my glasses."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/02.mp3'
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"Shiki-sama....?"
    
    "Are you not feeling well?\""
    
    "\".... No, I'm just a little tired from yesterday."
    
    "I'll be alright, so don't worry.\""
    
    "Lightly shaking my head, I clear my head of what I was seeing."
    
    ".... Last night, I forced myself to keep my promise with Arcueid, so my body isn't back to normal yet."
    
    "\"Good morning, Hisui."
    
    "Thanks for coming to wake me up, as always.\""
    
    "Sitting up in bed, I do my best to smile naturally."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T04.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"No, this is my duty."
    
    "There is no need for you to thank me, Shiki-sama.\""
    
    "\"Really, but I am grateful."
    
    "You are infinitely better than an alarm clock.\""
    
    "I stand up."
    
    "It's not yet seven o'clock---about ten minutes earlier than I usually get up."
    
    "\".... Hmm, breakfast?"
    
    "I'll be there soon, so please go ahead of me.\""
    
    "\"Yes, I will wait for you in the sitting room.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Giving a bow, Hisui exits the room."
    
    "----Well then."
    
    "I'm still feeling a little sluggish, but it's not too bad to skip school."
    
    "I'm sure after I eat the breakfast Kohaku-san prepared, I'll feel a lot better."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "As usual, Akiha is sitting on the sofa, and Hisui is waiting by the wall."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T04A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Good morning, Nii-san."
    
    "Did you sleep well last night?\""
    
    "Akiha greets me calmly as I enter the room."
    
    "She doesn't know I left last night."
    
    ".... Since she was so worried, I feel guilty for sneaking out."
    
    "\".... Yeah, good morning Akiha."
    
    "You're up early today, too.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T12A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"No, I'm like always.... Nii-san?\""
    
    "As if reading my mind, she looks directly at me."
    
    "\"Um----Is there something on my face, Akiha?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T17A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"No, that isn't it.... Nii-san, are you really alright?"
    
    "You still do not look well, so if you are still sick, maybe it is better if you just rest today----\""
    
    "----Oh, that's it."
    
    "I relax, realizing she did not find out about last night."
    
    "\"No, I'm really okay."
    
    "I'll be better sooner or later, so please don't look so worried.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T12A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\".... Okay."
    
    "If you say so, Nii-san, then I will not say anything.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "She goes quiet, still looking worried."
    
    "\"Hm, it's quite rare for you to be convinced this quickly."
    
    "It's not like you.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T21.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    "\"Hey, I'm always sensible."
    
    "I only warn you because you're the one with the problems."
    
    "So please do not blame me for your imperfections.\""
    
    "She glares at me."
    
    "\"Oh, that's more like it."
    
    "Hey, Hisui, doesn't it not feel like morning unless Akiha gets harsh?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T21.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    "\"................\""
    
    "Is it because I suddenly called out to her or because she doesn't know what to say?"
    
    "Hisui neither confirms nor denies my statement."
    
    "\"See?"
    
    "Look, Akiha, Hisui thinks so, too.\""
    
    "\"Don't be foolish."
    
    "Hisui doesn't say anything because she is surprised.\""
    
    "Wrinkling her forehead in a frown, Akiha glares again."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T03A.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    "\"Also, I've always wanted to say this, but you rely on Hisui too much."
    
    "You have been sleeping since yesterday, so it would have been fine if you woke up earlier."
    
    "But you always wake up late."
    
    "Are you slacking off because Hisui does not say anything?\""
    
    "\"Wha----You make it sound like I'm causing her trouble!\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T18A.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    "\"Not 'like', you are causing her trouble."
    
    "Hey, don't you think so, Hisui?\""
    
    "\"............\""
    
    "Hisui still doesn't say anything and stands there quietly."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T03A.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    "\"See?"
    
    "Hisui says she thinks so, too.\""
    
    "\"No way!"
    
    "She didn't say anything!\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T03A.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T04.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    "\"................\""
    
    "Hisui is silent."
    
    "But, her silence feels like she's agreeing more with Akiha."
    
    "\"........ Oogh.\""
    
    "I feel like it's now two against one."
    
    "\"Shiki-san."
    
    "Breakfast is ready~\""
    
    "With great timing, Kohaku-san's voice echoes through the room."
    
    "\"Um, I'm gonna go eat.\""
    
    "I quickly head towards the dining room."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T04.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(-24, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T08.png' as i1 at fgpos(126, 0)
    
    "\"................\""
    
    "I feel the silent pressure of the two behind me drilling into my back."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "After breakfast, I head back to the sitting room."
    
    "Akiha isn't there, and Hisui is the only one standing."
    
    "\"Huh?"
    
    "Akiha left for school already?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"Yes."
    
    "It is also time for you to go to school as well, Shiki-sama.\""
    
    "\"Ah, it's already twenty after?"
    
    "I guess I should get going soon.\""
    
    ".... To be honest, I still don't feel too good, but I'm sure I'll return to normal soon."
    
    "\"Sorry, Hisui, but can you get my bag from my room?"
    
    "I'm going to wash my face.\""
    
    "\"As you wish.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_48A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "After getting all my preparations done, I leave the mansion."
    
    "Holding my bag, Hisui sees me off at the entrance."
    
    "\"I'll be going."
    
    "I'm not sure when I'll be back, but probably by dinner.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_48A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T05.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"Yes, I will be waiting.\""
    
    "She gives a silent bow."
    
    ".... There's a trace of uneasiness in her face."
    
    "\"Hisui?"
    
    "Are you feeling sick?\""
    
    "\"No----it is not me, but you do not appear well."
    
    "I am unsure if it is a good idea to let you go.\""
    
    "She speaks hesitantly."
    
    "\"I'm alright."
    
    "I don't feel great, but just a little heavy."
    
    "Geez, both you and Akiha like to worry a lot.\""
    
    "\".... Is that so?"
    
    "If it is just us, then that will be fine, but..\""
    
    "\".... Geez."
    
    "I'll come back early today and rest, so that should be good, right?"
    
    "I won't overdo anything, so don't look like that.\""
    
    "\"........ Yes."
    
    "Forgive me, Shiki-sama.\""
    
    "She still looks very worried."
    
    "\"I'm off."
    
    "I'll be better by the time I get back, so please relax.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_48A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T07.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"Ah----Shiki-sama----\""
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_03.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "I ignore her and leave the mansion."
    
    "The image of Hisui watching me uneasily remains in my head."
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_22A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/03.mp3'
    
    "I head towards school."
    
    "My feet are heavy and it feels like I'm in another person's body as I head down the hill."
    
    ".... It's probably just the weariness from last night."
    
    "Even though I thought I would recover right away, the sluggishness doesn't fade."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_01A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "It's ten minutes until eight."
    
    "The school gate is flooded with arriving students."
    
    "\"---Ah.\""
    
    "By the gate, I see a familiar figure."
    
    "\".... Ciel.. Senpai.\""
    
    "It's a completely normal, morning scene."
    
    "But, what I saw that time----"
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/event/CEL_E04.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_01A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "If it wasn't for that, it would be a normal morning."
    
    "\"------\""
    
    "Not even knowing what I plan on doing, I chase after Senpai."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"Senpai!\""
    
    "I call after her."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "\"Oh, good morning, Tohno-kun."
    
    "It's strange meeting you out here.\""
    
    "\".... Yeah, I saw your figure from behind, so I ran after you, Senpai."
    
    "Um.... there was something I wanted to ask.\""
    
    "I sneak a look at her face."
    
    "\"Yes, what is it?\""
    
    "She faces me with her usual, gentle smile."
    
    "\".... Uh Senpai."
    
    "Two nights ago, were you near my house?"
    
    "In a black coat and a skirt flowing in the wind.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T12.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "\"....?"
    
    "What are you talking about?\""
    
    "\"Um....!"
    
    "well--yeah, the high-laced boots suited you."
    
    "I was kind of fascinated, you looked, really cool.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T05.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "....\"Huh?\" Senpai tilts her head."
    
    "She frowns like she doesn't understand my words completely, and then denies it."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "\"Um, I don't quite understand, but you're saying that I was near your house two nights ago, looking like that?\""
    
    "\"Yeah."
    
    "Senpai, that was you, right?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T10A.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "\"No way."
    
    "Tohno-kun, are you saying I look like I really have that much free time?\""
    
    "---Senpai is really angry."
    
    "She can't be playing dumb or lying."
    
    "\"Ah----No, that's not it, but I just.... saw someone that looked like you in park last night, so---\""
    
    "Senpai gives a sigh."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "\"Tohno-kun, that wasn't me."
    
    "I don't have that kind of hobby.\""
    
    "\"Ah---Yeah, I know."
    
    "I just wanted to ask.\""
    
    ".... Certainly after having her say that, she is right."
    
    "Ciel-senpai and the person that night aren't related at all."
    
    "In the first place, Senpai's just a normal person, and if she was actually there---she had to have seen me fight that bandaged guy with my knife."
    
    "If she saw such a gruesome scene, there'd be no way she could talk with me normally like this."
    
    "\".... Sorry, please forget about it."
    
    "I guess it was just someone else.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_03A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T09.png' as i0 at fgpos(52, 0)
    
    "\"That's fine, but.... did that person really look like me?"
    
    "That weird person?\""
    
    "\"Well, I'm not too sure."
    
    "It was dark, and far away........ huh?\""
    
    "Yeah, it was far and I couldn't make out her face."
    
    "So why did I think it looked like Senpai....?"
    
    "\".... Hmm.. Maybe there is something wrong with me.\""
    
    "I cross my arms and think."
    
    "Then, the ten minute bell rings."
    
    "\"---Crap, we'll be late."
    
    "Bye, Senpai, see you later!\""
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_06A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "I dash into my classroom."
    
    "It's still five minutes before class, so it's very noisy inside."
    
    "\"Arihiko, isn't here.\""
    
    "Knowing him, he'll probably come in around second period."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_06A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Lunch time."
    
    "It looks like Arihiko's not coming."
    
    ".... Inui Arihiko and Yumizuka Satsuki are the two people absent today."
    
    "Yumizuka Satsuki has caught a cold or something and she will be absent for a while."
    
    "\".... Senpai doesn't seem to be coming too, so I guess I'll eat by myself.\""
    
    "I say that, but I'm not hungry."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_11.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_06A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    ".... What is it?"
    
    "I didn't feel so good to begin with, but after coming to school, I feel a lot worse."
    
    "It's not just my body feeling heavy."
    
    "The scar on my chest is irritating; it's an annoying sensation."
    
    "\".... Maybe I shouldn't have come to school.\""
    
    ".... For a brief moment, I see the worrying faces of Hisui and Akiha in my mind."
    
    "Maybe the fact that I ignored Akiha's wishes for me to rest last night and instead went to see Arcueid might've caused this."
    
    "Being worn out by just sitting, I start to feel a strange uneasiness."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    jump s107a
